document_data.name: Winter Walk
document_data.mainbody: '''Winter Walk''' was a small street located in the city of [[Zhentil Keep]] during the mid-14{{th}} century [[DR]].
document_data.Location: Winter Walk was located in western Zhentil Keep in the [[Zhentil Keep/Common Quarter|Common Quarter]]. It originated on [[Nool Street]] in the west near the city's exterior wall, then passed east until it connected with [[Dixon Street]]. [[Silver Street]] intersected Winter Walk near its origin.
document_data.Description: The road was quite small at {{SI|300|ft|long=yes}} in length.
